title: Messiah Trilogy
description:
The entire Messiah trilogy (Messiah Complex, Messiah War and Second Coming) gathered and organized by reading order, plus Necrosha. I just compiled the issues, so thanks to all the scanners and up-loaders.
Also, thank you various engineers, software developers and scientists for inventing the internet, scanners and peer-to-peer file sharing. 
Thank you comic artists and writers. Remember, you like=you buy. Unless you poor. Or cheap.
